 .toMat(Sink.seq)(Keep.both)\n      .run()(materializer)\n\n    killSwitch.shutdown()\n\n    assertThat(await(streamResult).toList.asJava).isEmpty()\n  }\n\n  private def withActorSystem(testName: String)(testBody: ActorSystem => Unit): Unit = {\n"}]}
